        "## Load Dataset\n",
        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Load a suitable dataset for object recognition that is compatible with YOLO. This might involve downloading publicly available datasets like COCO or preparing a custom dataset with YOLO-specific annotation formats.\n"
